{"tid":164513,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（2017年3月下旬）東北季候風為本港帶來較涼天氣","createTime":"2017-03-20T16:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T16:56:28.000Z","uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a07064fb35f20aa40a8b5ed9e4109f1b48fa51b","tid":164513,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk017&h=0677eeb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣象討論：2017年3月下旬</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2017年3月21日至31日</span></strong></span><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">&lt;ins&gt;◤溫度術語&lt;/ins&gt;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;ins&gt;◤參考網頁&lt;/ins&gt;</span></span><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5cbf58d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1f7ed532\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ed4b4ec7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=deb76722\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 香港天文台電腦預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fnhm%2Fnhm_uc.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1f575c3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7bc7764c\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/SuV1UB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FSuV1UB&h=aa5b9639&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1mOf5kb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1mOf5kb&h=f43ed746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a5ticH&h=b05f53f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ahInaZ&h=2a1d8db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ajChbn&h=22f823b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ap2lTE&h=475ff2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a7TpCM&h=ef01e17d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2F1Oc5V&h=2e7774ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FMeu94L&h=e469b653&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FpSSahs&h=61ae872d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">氣象台專頁正式登場</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>我們自2008年起發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5422d022\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=40102abb\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/UTube\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FUTube&h=a22db7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=efe12a2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a></em></strong>"},{"pid":"b8c908d04a69c687213d70bc42ae854f98ef2522","tid":164513,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3703d9b5b8711599f6544fa9ed6897044f76b6b4","tid":164513,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:06:59.000Z","msg":"係咪應該改名？"},{"pid":"9b51050b51240134cf499912ab5aee1e5d58e5c0","tid":164513,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"期待下星期天氣仲有得轉涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee4ca1e6d83b21550ad9c85c8284167d9ba2020","tid":164513,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T22:37:56.000Z","msg":"本 港 地 區 今 日 天 氣 預 測 <br />\n<br />\n早 晚 沿 岸 有 霧 。 日 間 部 分 時 間 有 陽 光 ， 天 氣 溫 暖 ，<strong> 最 高 氣 溫 約 27 度</strong> 。 吹 微 風 ， 晚 上 轉 吹 清 勁 東 風 ， 有 一 兩 陣 雨 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3cfa516df44fd03f1d8cc4c67da41aa617573f","tid":164513,"uid":5293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T22:40:10.000Z","msg":"邊撚度涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f13dedf6a9bda8dc9ec4a5d3fa877a